  "texts": [
    "Privacy and security challengesThe COVID-19 pandemic has highlighted the need for a thorough investigation into the security and privacy of personal data.",
    "The Zoom video conferencing app scandal highlights the need for privacy and security measures.",
    "Authorities may request personal information like GPS location, CT scans, and daily activities to control the situation and make informed decisions.",
    "However, people often resist sharing their personal information, highlighting the trade-off between privacy and performance.",
    "Various technologies are available to address these privacy and security issues, and these could serve as research directives for future research [188,189]."
  ]
